description:
People draw to express what's on their mind. I used to draw so much as a kid; but it'd never satisfied me fully. Because my goal has been telling stories through my art & the base of a good story is a strong character which I can turn myself into billions.
Now they have come as comic-quality NFTs which you can collect!

These are "self-comic" series and of course it's my first time that I mint NFT.
